OL,5, Adidas is being sued by investors who  
OL,6, claim the firm knew about Kanye West's 
OL,7, problematic behaviour years before it  
OL,8, ended their partnership.               
OL,10,FInvestors allege Adidas failed to limit
OL,11,Ffinancial losses and take precautionary
OL,12,Fmeasures to minimise their exposure.   
OL,14,FThe sportswear giant ended its         
OL,15,Fcollaboration with the designer and    
OL,16,Frapper, who is known as Ye, last year  
OL,17,Ffollowing antisemitic comments.        
OL,19,FIn response, Adidas said: "We outright 
OL,20,Freject these unfounded claims."        
